Summary: Multiple orange lights moving in the east and southeastern horizon
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home and my father called me to look outside. I had recently been investigating some strange activity near my house over the past week, so I ran outside to see. I had no idea what they were, and still don't. There were probably 6-10 I saw in total, seemingly appearing, moving from one point to another in straight lines, and then disappearing. This being my third sighting in the sky, I wasn't afraid like before. I was elated, actually, and excited at what I was seeing. Soon they all disappeared, there numbers dwindling down.
